        <h2>
            国学课的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 2 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1935315">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1935315/" class="title-link">这本台湾的国学教科书本质上主要是书目和内容提纲</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1935315"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/tongueear/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2058942-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tongueear/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">舌耳</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-03-30"
      class="main-meta">2009-03-30 14:54:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1935315_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本台湾的国学教科书本质上主要是书目和内容提纲  有意思之处在于将它拿来和大陆的语文历史教学提纲来比较 一对比就明白了 就像中学的时候历史课下课以后翻阅剑桥插图中国史的相应章节，深刻的体会到那种戏剧化的差别 历史是人为的历史，历史即伪历史

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1935315/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1935315_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1935315_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1427285">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1427285/" class="title-link">台湾的书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1427285"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lazyzhsh/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1453797-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lazyzhsh/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">lazyzhsh</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-07-03"
      class="main-meta">2008-07-03 11:32:23</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1427285_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                     第一次在图书馆的一个角落里看到了这本书，挺惊讶的。大陆也开始有人关注台湾的语文教育体系了（应该是国文吧）。    其实想想也对，小时候我们接受了九年的义务教育，但回头想来那些幼年时在心中留下的其实是一个个红色文学家的一串串文字而已，而真正的一个价值体系并没有...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1427285/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1427285_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1427285_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










